sql: SELECT MAX(Book_ID) FROM book WHERE  Author_ID != 3

SELECT Age FROM author JOIN book ON author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE book.Author_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Author_ID < (SELECT MIN(Author_ID) FROM author AS s WHERE  s.Age > 43 LIMIT 3) ORDER BY Age DESC LIMIT 10

SELECT COUNT(book.Author_ID), book.Press_ID FROM book JOIN book AS u ON book.Book_ID = u.Book_ID WHERE  u.Book_ID >= 25 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM press WHERE  Year_Profits_billion > 20 AND book.Book_ID = Press_ID) ORDER BY book.Press_ID DESC
SELECT book.Author_ID, Sale_Amount FROM author JOIN book JOIN press ON book.Press_ID = press.Press_ID AND author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE  Month_Profits_billion = 11
SELECT MAX(x.Age), x.Gender, x.Name FROM author AS x WHERE  x.Age <= 77 OR Name NOT IN (SELECT Name FROM author WHERE  Author_ID >= 49 LIMIT 2)
SELECT press.Name FROM author JOIN book JOIN press ON book.Press_ID = press.Press_ID AND author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE  book.Press_ID <= 32
SELECT AVG(z.Age) FROM author AS z WHERE z.Age BETWEEN 1 AND 10
SELECT MAX(Author_ID), Gender FROM author WHERE  Author_ID < 7 AND Name NOT IN (SELECT Name FROM author AS e WHERE  e.Author_ID > 55) LIMIT 6

SELECT AVG(press.Press_ID) FROM author JOIN book JOIN press ON book.Press_ID = press.Press_ID AND author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE  press.Press_ID > 76 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM author WHERE book.Book_ID = Author_ID)
SELECT MAX(Author_ID), Author_ID FROM book JOIN press ON book.Press_ID = press.Press_ID WHERE  book.Press_ID > 58 ORDER BY Author_ID DESC
SELECT AVG(Age), Book_Series FROM author JOIN book ON author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE Name NOT IN (SELECT Name FROM author WHERE Author_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10) LIMIT 8
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT y.Age), y.Author_ID, y.Age, y.Gender FROM author AS y WHERE  y.Author_ID <= 34 GROUP BY y.Gender HAVING AVG(y.Author_ID) <= 92
SELECT MAX(Year_Profits_billion) FROM press WHERE Month_Profits_billion IN (SELECT Month_Profits_billion FROM press AS g WHERE g.Month_Profits_billion BETWEEN 1 AND 10) LIMIT 4
SELECT Name, Name FROM press WHERE Name NOT IN (SELECT Name FROM author AS s WHERE  s.Author_ID = 65) ORDER BY Name DESC
SELECT COUNT(Press_ID), Author_ID FROM book WHERE Book_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Title > (SELECT MAX(Title) FROM book WHERE  Author_ID = 49)
SELECT MAX(Author_ID) FROM book WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM press WHERE  Year_Profits_billion != 34 AND book.Book_ID = Press_ID LIMIT 9)

SELECT Year_Profits_billion, Sale_Amount, Release_date FROM author JOIN book JOIN press ON book.Press_ID = press.Press_ID AND author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE  author.Author_ID > 63 GROUP BY Release_date LIMIT 6

SELECT press.Month_Profits_billion, v.Month_Profits_billion, v.Year_Profits_billion FROM press AS v JOIN press ON press.Press_ID = v.Press_ID WHERE press.Year_Profits_billion BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY v.Year_Profits_billion ORDER BY v.Month_Profits_billion ASC
SELECT MAX(Age), SUM(Age), COUNT(DISTINCT Author_ID) FROM author WHERE  Age < 85 LIMIT 7
SELECT AVG(h.Month_Profits_billion), SUM(h.Press_ID), h.Name FROM press AS h WHERE  h.Year_Profits_billion != 37 ORDER BY h.Name ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Release_date), Gender FROM author JOIN book JOIN press ON book.Press_ID = press.Press_ID AND author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE  Age > 84 GROUP BY Gender HAVING MAX(Book_ID) < 56 ORDER BY Gender ASC
SELECT Press_ID, Name FROM press WHERE Year_Profits_billion > (SELECT MIN(Year_Profits_billion) FROM press AS j)
SELECT SUM(Book_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT Book_ID) FROM author JOIN book ON author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE  author.Author_ID = 92 LIMIT 7
SELECT t.Gender FROM author AS t WHERE  t.Age != 42 LIMIT 7
SELECT f.Name FROM author AS f
SELECT Press_ID FROM press WHERE  Month_Profits_billion <= 22
SELECT COUNT(Year_Profits_billion), Month_Profits_billion FROM press GROUP BY Month_Profits_billion
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Press_ID), Name FROM press WHERE  Year_Profits_billion != 47 GROUP BY Name HAVING COUNT(Year_Profits_billion) = 58 ORDER BY Name ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Name), book.Author_ID, Book_Series FROM author JOIN book ON author.Author_ID = book.Author_ID WHERE Age BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY Book_Series DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT u.Press_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT u.Sale_Amount), COUNT(DISTINCT u.Book_ID), u.Press_ID FROM book AS u WHERE  u.Press_ID = 64 GROUP BY u.Press_ID HAVING MIN(u.Press_ID) <= 58 ORDER BY u.Press_ID ASC
SELECT MIN(Month_Profits_billion), Name FROM press WHERE Press_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Month_Profits_billion < 3 LIMIT 8
SELECT COUNT(c.Age), c.Name, c.Age FROM author AS c WHERE c.Author_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  c.Age <= 85 GROUP BY c.Age
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT d.Book_Series), d.Press_ID FROM book AS d WHERE  d.Press_ID = 34 GROUP BY d.Press_ID
